snippet.title: Sonic 3 A.I.R. Full Game Release Clip
snippet.description:
And here we go with the full game.

Before downloading, please make sure you have the Steam version of Sonic 3 & Knuckles installed, which Sonic 3 A.I.R. is built upon.

Download from the project homepage:
https://sonic3air.org

For more info and updates follow me on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/Eukaryot3K
